    <string name="setting_keepalive_guide_generic">For more reliable push delivery:\n\n1. Disable battery optimization for Gotify.\n2. Allow notifications and background activity.\n3. Avoid force stopping the app.\n4. Keep the foreground service notification enabled.\n\nAndroid may still stop background network connections on some devices.</string>
    <string name="setting_keepalive_guide_xiaomi">For Xiaomi/Redmi/POCO devices:\n\n1. Battery saver → set Gotify to No restrictions.\n2. Enable Auto start for Gotify.\n3. Allow notifications and background activity.\n4. Do not force stop the app.\n5. Keep the foreground service notification enabled.\n\nSome MIUI/HyperOS versions may still stop background connections after task cleanup.</string>
